---
title: Meatless Linda McCartney Meatballs & Spaghetti With Grated Cheese & Tomato Sauce
description: Spaghetti and meatballs. What’s not to love? This veggie twist on the classic is packed with a thick tomatoey saucre, fresh yellow pepper and shallot. Buon appetito.
